messages.content: You are analyzing Terms of Service. Extract important clauses about privacy, data collection, liability, fees, and user rights. Respond ONLY with valid JSON: {"highlights": ["clause1", "clause2", ...]}

This is part 3 of 3 of a Terms of Service. Extract important clauses:

 makes sense for this service
This service is only available to users over a certain age
If you are the target of a copyright claim, your content may be removed
Your personal data is aggregated into statistics
The service does not guarantee accuracy or reliability of the information provided
Provides instructions on how to submit a copyright claim
Invalidity of any portion of the Terms of Service does not entail invalidity of its remainder
This service requires first-party cookies
You cannot distribute or disclose your account to third parties
Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision
Users agree not to use the service for illegal purposes
You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account
This service does not guarantee that it or the products obtained through it meet the users' expectations or requirements
Third parties may be involved in operating the service
This service collects your IP address for location use
Users agree to comply with the law of the service's country
This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header.
